{"tid":1826180,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【高質短片】香港要靠東江水的由來","createTime":"2020-01-16T02:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T03:15:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b936edbcad304d6f5298efdb5648618ee319716","tid":1826180,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:14:59.000Z","msg":"東江水供水協議將於今年到期，料必加價。<br />\n<br />\n今日，香港高度依賴東江水，但其實戰後，本地曾誕生過不少世界第一的水利工程。香港中文大學政治與行政學系講師李家翹形容：「我想港英最瘋狂的計劃，是建核能海水化淡廠，當時還是冷戰時期。」<br />\n<br />\n60 年代，面對嚴重水荒，港英政府為何拒絕中國的免費水，堅持要掏庫房買水？東江水供港，又何以由一宗低調買賣，演變成現在中港關係的最強文宣？最貼近民生的用水，背後仍然是一場又一場的政治角力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UuwEV8ZbDe8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUuwEV8ZbDe8&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=5163a805\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UuwEV8ZbDe8</a><br />\n鳴謝：政府檔案處歷史檔案館 資料提供<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/01/16/water-policies/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2Fwater-policies%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=52eab6fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/01/16/water-policies/</a>"},{"pid":"63c781027ab9a23e954bc4c04e6c530e6eef7c78","tid":1826180,"uid":178364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:18:44.000Z","msg":"香港曾經有全球最大嘅海水化淡廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未來都要有！"},{"pid":"2aafded9cee30c237ef039f2726490c42b3c561c","tid":1826180,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:15:23.000Z","msg":"送錢比支那<br />\n再放走東江水"}]}